	</p>
	<!-- /post-meta -->
	
	
<!-- post-image -->
<!-- /post-image -->

<!-- post-content -->

	<p>While Facebook is an active, fast-paced site of social engagement for roughly one billion people, it also constitutes a staggering archive – the database of all posts, pictures, likes, friendships and associations, and interactions. The interface design of Facebook gives but a small peek into the workings of the complex databases beneath, and the lives(&#8230;)</p>

